Package mainmenu

This package contains multiple class files required to create a Pong game.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisplayScore
    Constructor that controls the score positioning and display of the score elements.
    explAnim
    This class controls the sprite animation of the explosion.
    explAnim1
    This class controls the sprite animation of the explosion.
    MainMenu
    This class represents the pong game done in javafx.
    Pong3
    This class represents the pong game logic with all the animations.
    ScoreKeeper
    This class keeps the players' scores of the pong game.
    SoundPlayer
    This class represents the sound player which plays the collision sounds as well as various music in the pong game.

Package mainmenu Description

This package contains multiple class files required to create a Pong game. The game has 2 difficulty levels and animations to keep the score and explosions when the ball misses the player's paddle. Sound effects are included to make a better game experience.

Date: 13 April, 2016

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Maksym Kolov, Neil Patel, Austin Mclemore
